# Environment Variables Template

Copy file ini ke `.env.local` (frontend) atau `.env` (backend) dan isi nilainya.
File `.env.local` sudah ada di .gitignore — aman.

---

## Frontend (.env.local)

```env
# Backend API URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

# NextAuth (Phase 2 - Auth)
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your-secret-here
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Google OAuth (Phase 2)
AUTH_GOOGLE_ID=your-google-client-id
AUTH_GOOGLE_SECRET=your-google-client-secret
```

## Backend (.env)

```env
# CORS
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000

# Database (Phase 2)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@localhost:5432/finance_analyzer

# JWT (Phase 2)
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret

# AI Provider (Phase AI)
AI_PROVIDER=deepseek
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your-deepseek-key
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-key

# Payment (Phase 6)
MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY=your-midtrans-key
MIDTRANS_CLIENT_KEY=your-midtrans-client-key
MIDTRANS_IS_PRODUCTION=false
```

> Lihat SECRETS.md (lokal, tidak di-commit) untuk nilai production lengkap.
